channel.title: Javac problem
channel.description:
Everytime I try to compile, this shows up. [img]http://img88.imageshack.us/img88/836/wtfhaxomfgqt4.png[/img]
I recently got JDK6u6, so I put these in my computer properties.
CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_06\bin;%CLASSPATH%; C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_06\bin
Is there anything else I need to do?
